urlLink Medicare Bill Would Enrich Companies (washingtonpost.com)   By Amy Goldstein  Washington Post Staff Writer  Monday, November 24, 2003; Page A01       The Medicare legislation that passed the House near dawn on Saturday and is moving toward a final vote in the Senate would steer at least $125 billion over the next decade in extra assistance to the health care industry and U.S. businesses, in addition to its widely heralded goal of helping older Americans pay for prescription drugs.